description:
Two lost boys, Black and White, wander the mean streets of Treasure Town, a surreal metropolis of mimes, freaks, crooks, cops, drifters, and down-and-outers.

Chapter Titles

  • Skirmish One: Welcome To Our Monkey House
  • Skirmish Two: Paving the Road To Hell
  • Skirmish Three: Cat and Rat and Dog and City
  • Skirmish Four: Beware of Midnight Strolls
  • Skirmish Five: Getting Wilder Now, Getting Stronger Now
  • Skirmish Six: The Best of Times, The Worst of Times
  • Skirmish Seven: White Cries
  • Skirmish Eight: City of Blood, Night of Stars
  • Skirmish Nine: Black Flies
  • Skirmish Ten: Kimura Is A Loser
  • Skirmish Eleven: Treasure Town Waltz

description: Life as a Templar Knight returning from the Crusades is dull - bread, beans, and lots and lots of walking. But after Martin stumbles upon his lost love (now married to someone else), things begin to get more interesting very quickly. There's a vast conspiracy afoot to destroy the Templar Order and steal their treasure. Soon, Martin finds himself one of the only Templars out of prison - and out for revenge! The first volume in a trilogy written by Jordan Mechner, the creator of the acclaimed Prince of Persia video games.
